
HOW TO INSTALL SDC (OR TRITON ELASTIC CONTAINER INFRASTRUCTURE) OPEN SOURCE EDITION
0. what you need
	a USB key of 8GB or more
	one headnode server (X86_64, VX-T support, two NICs, 16GB RAM minimal, 10GB SAS/SATA disk minimal)
	one or more compute node server

1. preparation

	Download latest usg img:
		https://us-east.manta.joyent.com/Joyent_Dev/public/SmartDataCenter/usb-latest.tgz

	uncompress the tar ball

	write the img file to USB 
		Windows: https://docs.joyent.com/private-cloud/install/installation-media/windows
		Linux: https://docs.joyent.com/private-cloud/install/installation-media/linux
		MacOS: https://docs.joyent.com/private-cloud/install/installation-media/mac-osx
		SmartOS: https://docs.joyent.com/private-cloud/install/installation-media/smartos

